Recommendations:
We recommended to management and is agreeable to the following:
Conduct a strategic planning and evaluation of the procurement planning process in conformity with the provisions Section 10 of the 2016 RIRR of RA No. 9184;
As the end-user, require the VP for Administration of TCC to be responsible for the prompt preparation of all documents necessary for the procurement activity in conformity with Section 7.3. of the same RIRR of RA No. 9184.  Also direct such official to submit justification as to why the bidding only ensued after the payment of services and why it is still being practiced in CY 2023;
Ensure that the BAC observe strict adherence to RA No. 9184 regarding competitive bidding of the procurement of security services prior to engaging such services. This includes familiarizing the key personnel involved with the specific requirements and procedures outlined in the law; and
Before certifying as to the completeness of the documents on the Disbursement Voucher, require the Municipal Accountant to strengthen internal controls and employ oversight mechanisms to detect and prevent irregularities in expenditure.

